:"","name":"Tatum Dagelet","primary":true}}]}},"person_973385_translations":{"at":1773297823557,"data":{"id":973385,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ross Shor Lynch is an American actor, singer, and musician. He was the lead vocalist of the pop rock band R5 and is one half of the band The Driver Era (with his brother Rocky Lynch). As an actor, he rose to recognition for his debut role as Austin Moon on Disney Channel's comedy television series Austin & Ally and for his role as Brady in the network's Teen Beach Movie film series.\n\nIn 2017, Lynch starred in the biopic My Friend Dahmer as a teenage Jeffrey Dahmer. In 2018, he starred in Status Update as Kyle. Between 2018 and 2020, he starred as Harvey Kinkle in the Netflix series Chilling Adventures of Sabrina.","name":"Ross Lynch","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Ross Shor Lynch (29 de diciembre de 1995) es un actor, cantante, músico, compositor y bailarín estadounidense. Lynch es uno de los miembros fundadores de la banda de pop rock R5 y The Driver Era. Es más conocido por su papel de Austin Moon en la exitosa serie juvenil de Disney Channel, Austin & Ally.2​ En 2013, protagonizó la película de Disney Channel Teen Beach Movie interpretando a Brady, y su secuela.\n\nEn 2017, Lynch participó en la película My Friend Dahmer, en donde protagonizó al joven Jeffrey Dahmer. Desde 2018, interpreta a Harvey Kinkle en serie de Netflix Chilling Adventures of Sabrina, basada en el comic book del mismo nombre.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Ross Shor Lynch é um cantor, compositor e ator americano.  Ele é um dos membros fundadores da banda de pop rock R5.  Como ator, ele é conhecido por seu papel de estréia como Austin Moon na série original do Disney Channel Austin & Ally, e por seu papel como Brady na série Teen Beach Movie.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Росс Линч","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"罗斯·林奇（Ross Lynch），1995年12月29日出生在美国科罗拉多州利特尔顿，美国男演员。","name":"罗斯·林奇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"羅斯·林奇（Ross Lynch），1995 年 12 月 29 日出生在美國科羅拉多州利特爾頓，美國男演員。","name":"羅斯·林奇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"راس لینچ","primary":false}}]}}}}